<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        {{> home/sideMenu password=true}}
        <div class="col-xs-19">
            <div class="bg-white shadow p-h-lg user-main-h">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xs-24">
                        <div class="line">
                            <span class="f-gray f-s-20"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock m-r-xs"></span>修改密码</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-24 m-t-lg">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xs-24">
                                <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
                                    如果您是手机 + 验证码 或者 第三方帐号(腾讯、新浪微博等)登录且尚未设定旧密码，可以点击
                                    <a href="#" class="alert-link">重设密码</a>链接.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xs-12">
                                <form class="form-horizontal">
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-xs-6">旧密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-xs-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="请输入旧密码">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-xs-6">新密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-xs-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="请输入新密码，限6~20字符">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <label class="control-label col-xs-6">确认新密码</label>
                                        <div class="col-xs-18">
                                            <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="限6~20字符">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-group m-t-lg">
                                        <div class="col-xs-offset-11 col-xs-4">
                                            <button class="btn btn-success">确认修改</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>